Text:
Thank you good sir. Keep up the excellent work.

Gentlemen, the corporations have declared war on us with their conception of ACTA. This will end our way of life. Everything that we do or say will be monitored by cruel, calculating corporations who care only about their fat asses. We will fight them, we will utterly destroy them, and we will show them no mercy when we eliminate them and their hideous brood.

Gentlemen, we will visit their transgressions to their fourth and fifth generations, and we will be ruthless like they have been to us. Good luck gentlemen.
A=10, V=10.. Good torrent.. Excellent episode.. :)
